extends layout

block content
  h1 RideFlex Pro, #{firstName}! 🎉
  
  p We're absolutely thrilled to have you join our growing community of riders and drivers!
  
  p Here's what you can do with your new account:
  
  ul
    li 🚗 <strong>Book rides instantly</strong> - Get a ride in minutes
    li 📍 <strong>Real-time tracking</strong> - Track your driver's location
    li ⭐ <strong>Rate and review</strong> - Help improve our community
    li 💳 <strong>Secure payments</strong> - Multiple payment options
    li 📱 <strong>24/7 support</strong> - We're here to help anytime
  
  p Ready to get started? Click the button below to explore your dashboard:
  
  p(style='text-align: center;')
    a.button(href=url) Get Started Now
  
  p
    strong Getting started is easy:
  ol
    li Complete your profile
    li Add a payment method
    li Book your first ride
  
  p If you have any questions or need assistance, don't hesitate to reach out to our support team. We're here to make your experience as smooth as possible.
  
  p Welcome aboard! 
    br
    | The Uber Clone Team
  
  hr(style='margin: 30px 0; border: none; border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;')
  
  p(style='font-size: 14px; color: #666;')
    | <strong>Pro tip:</strong> Download our mobile app for the best experience! 📱
